{"tid":1480350,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲人自己都寸鳩喺香港機場發爛咋個澳洲遊客","createTime":"2019-08-17T09:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T10:44:20.000Z","uid":43785,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"98eb06300f10127daa824d1d1f866323719819c1","tid":1480350,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:18:59.000Z","msg":"澳洲人自己都寸鳩喺香港機場發爛咋個澳洲遊客<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nkP22EF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnkP22EF.jpg&h=a04e7c7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe Apologise For The Inconvenience | David Pope 15.8.19<br />\n<br />\n當日出post都講左好小事，注意到下次留意唔好再亂搞就得，係個日班友喊苦喊忽要生要死，又話輸清光，急住出黎幫兄弟道歉。<br />\n連出名大愛包容嘅澳洲人都寸你班民心黨和理非，好檢討下啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，冇事啦， 外國媒體都支持我哋<br />\n唔好你個傻閪旅客，<br />\n813我地捉間諜，打大陸人， 喺黑警手上搶人， 嚇到警察舉真槍， 所有知名既國際媒體都幫緊香港示威者， 呢鋪贏到盡呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我嫌做得唔夠盡咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c1a3874d16d0845ca83bdb376d7e43cd775fea","tid":1480350,"uid":43785,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:19:24.000Z","msg":"點都好， 特朗普已經做緊嘢 ，聽日818我地停一次， 黑衫，帶齊裝備（唔好戴）行出黎， 一百萬人去維園和平行一次出嚟。"},{"pid":"57aef57e91b82c5cc5e9029aa681509233d89f26","tid":1480350,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:19:39.000Z","msg":"old news is so...."},{"pid":"e011f1a14092974df877d23fec39e58ec91b1b9a","tid":1480350,"uid":43785,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UohgnH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUohgnH7.jpg&h=ad4848b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事實就係和理非當日攞住件發爛咋澳洲遊客話捉公安嘅人係鬼，如果講分化，咁當日班和理非就係分化。人哋覺得小事，一部份係示威者態度，另一部份就係見示威罷工塞呢樣塞個樣多過你食飯，係啲人未見識過驚青先會嗌塞機場輸哂。"},{"pid":"9ca77402ce8bf765036bf561a1a0a86e9aa08602","tid":1480350,"uid":153151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fbaJNac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfbaJNac.png&h=208c73ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf28a28995a403b4df260efb96842773d955342f","tid":1480350,"uid":75156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:21:58.000Z","msg":"鳩sir 你當更依幾日都無用手機咩 咁耐既野都攞返出黎講？<br />\n<br />\n依家講緊<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818 維園見啵</span></span>"},{"pid":"76dc4ae1e024243a30a1b536bceb29d5a64a2751","tid":1480350,"uid":242728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ca77402ce8bf765036bf561a1a0a86e9aa08602","tid":1480350,"uid":153151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fbaJNac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfbaJNac.png&h=208c73ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c551ba878660abff4200202bacca6aaaeb94d1","tid":1480350,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:23:09.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借位～<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保護自己資產，全民唱美元現鈔！</strong></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1478882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1478882</a>"},{"pid":"417249b01898f6793f5cb6c000b825f009662e03","tid":1480350,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:27:22.000Z","msg":"民意撚出黎講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d27c5ff13723d0fe1bd4ea99d9b586ae7931b2","tid":1480350,"uid":158317,"l